    "asOf": "2025-11-06",
    "date": "2026-04-24T22:21:45Z",
    "text": "VA Zero Suicide Demonstration Project Act of 2025\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to establish the Zero Suicide Initiative pilot program for the purpose of improving safety and suicide care for veterans. The program must be implemented at five VA medical centers, including one that serves veterans in rural and remote areas."
